Examples are available in

https://solps-mdsplus.aug.ipp.mpg.de/repos/SOLPS/trunk/solps_examples/solps-iter/bench_mark

To see what is available:

svn list https://solps-mdsplus.aug.ipp.mpg.de/repos/SOLPS/trunk/solps_examples/solps-iter/

produces

bench_mark/

amongst others, and

svn list https://solps-mdsplus.aug.ipp.mpg.de/repos/SOLPS/trunk/solps_examples/solps-iter/bench_mark

produces

AUG_16151_D/
AUG_16151_D+C+He/
...

To install the bench_mark cases, do:

svn checkout https://solps-mdsplus.aug.ipp.mpg.de/repos/SOLPS/trunk/solps_examples/solps-iter/bench_mark bench_mark

in this directory.
